{"lemma":"ساحَةٌ","slug":"ساحَةٌ","root":"س.#.ح","root_slug":"س-_-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/س-_-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n21151","n21394"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"field, area"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"yard, court, courtyard"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Borrowed from Egyptian sḫt (“field, open country”). Unrelated to سَاحَ (sāḥa, “to travel”) if that sense as opposed to “to run, to melt” is not denominal from the present noun. Compare رِيف (rīf, “countryside, rural land”) also borrowed from Egyptian."},"ipa":["/saː.ħa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n21151","headword_ar":"سَاحَةٌ","root":"swH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sawaHapN","text_ar":"سَوَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"court,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"open area,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a spacious vacant part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is no building;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaroSapN","text_ar":"عَرْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is no building nor roof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 33:) its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAHap","text_ar":"بَاحَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or its"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a spacious place in front"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a house: (Msb in the present art.:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spacious, place, among the dwellings of a tribe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a side, region, quarter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a lateral,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an outward"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjacent, part"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAHiyapN","text_ar":"نَاحِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the pl. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAHN","text_ar":"سَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather this is a coll. gen. n. of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sAHp","text_ar":"ساحة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.] and [the pl. is]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saAHaAtN","text_ar":"سَاحَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwHN","text_ar":"سُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) the last like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"budonN","text_ar":"بُدْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badanapN","text_ar":"بَدَنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu$obN","text_ar":"خُشْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xa$abapN","text_ar":"خَشَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwayoHapN","text_ar":"سُوَيْحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also 7 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"syH","text_ar":"سيح"},{"kind":"text","text":".] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eamara A@ll~`hu saAHataka","text_ar":"عَمَرَ ا@للّٰهُ سَاحَتَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May God people thy court,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yard;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"make it to be well stocked with people and the like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And in a case of drought you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHomar~a","text_ar":"اِحْمَرَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~uwHu waA@gubar~a A@ls~uwHu","text_ar":"ا@للُّوحُ وَا@غُبَرَّ ا@لسُّوحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The air,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"atmosphere, has become red, and the courts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yards, have become very dusty"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu labariYo'u Als~aAHapi","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَبَرِىْءُ السَّاحَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", a phrase like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu labariYo'u AlEa*irapi","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَبَرِىْءُ العَذِرَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E*r","text_ar":"عذر"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E*r","text_ar":"عذر"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n21394","headword_ar":"سَاحَةٌ","root":"syH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 7; and see also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swH","text_ar":"سوح"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}